Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西在我身体里抽动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人用温暖的眼神望着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:26.14,staff2,NTP,0,0,0,,壳中小鸟 第2话「结城怜」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个少女的什么地方吸引了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比喻来说的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她的纯洁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像磁铁异性相吸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引着肮脏的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在这几个月里她到底在等谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着急呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是应该还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上进行治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有地方去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:03:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有钱了 只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没关系 你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的胃好像不是这么说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珐姆 是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡觉的时候叫了很多次 珐姆 珐姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过段时间要变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里肯定是住不了了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 爸爸回来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我没有地方可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 要不要跟我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 东洋人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来还很小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦您了 让她在这里待一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会好好工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能帮您的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫结城怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是短时间 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要住在德雷特家 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要遵守我们这儿的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜 今天开始这里就是你的房间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有事情要调查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们照顾怜两三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 弄得这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那 调查的结果怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满足条件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 有事我会再拜托你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您找我吗 德雷特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你工作很勤奋呢 怜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您父亲那里有消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 父亲那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快去自己的房间见他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到父亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲果然来找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怜 我好想你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快让我看看 真的是怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好可爱啊 怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 父亲 好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 父亲 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 真正的父亲到底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 已经 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 柯蕾娅 你都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 先让她静静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊 旧报纸?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被带进车站的男女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同死亡 男人死亡 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸存的少女意识不清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑发 眼睛是绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过 不要对我做的事指手画脚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子住在这个宅子里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是让她遵守这里的规矩让她接客了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她来这里的时候就在你面前跟我约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要做好你自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 如果我再小心一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的事情全部忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像以前德雷特说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人也有各种各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有喜欢你的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有喜欢怜的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有忘记跟你的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脚张开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就变乖巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又要对你另眼相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是老板啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真是可爱的小姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 您还满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 应该会有一个愉快的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那您慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许转开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就由你来服侍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该没有教过你这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下那个 怜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以了吧 快丢掉那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我要去找父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.97,0:25:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要忘记过去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.81,0:25:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温暖的回忆只要再重新创造就好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.46,0:26:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.07,0:26:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 头发
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.82,0:26:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜拜托我剪的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.14,0:26:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我再待一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.54,0:26:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.06,0:26:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.17,0:26:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事了啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.10,0:26:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.23,0:26:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-柯蕾娅 \N-嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.32,0:26:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珐姆是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.21,0:27:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是建了这个院子的人哦